      "content": "<p class=\"c10\"><span class=\"c8\"></span></p><ul class=\"c6 lst-kix_nap7staus29z-0 start\" data-indent=\"0\"><li class=\"c9 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c8\">Copy the article Title xxx reports bit below and paste it somewhere to make a new article</span></li><li class=\"c9 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c8\">Write your article</span></li></ul><ul class=\"c6 lst-kix_nap7staus29z-1 start\" data-indent=\"1\"><li class=\"c2 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c8\">Use headings from h2 to h5</span></li></ul><ul class=\"c6 lst-kix_nap7staus29z-2 start\" data-indent=\"2\"><li class=\"c7 li-bullet-0\"><span style=\"overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 346.00px; height: 719.00px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"images/APuouOfxZhoMoCjiaVUOERIT4cJOnoMUx8DgM91hS3InkLRYdH7hVi-3NxL4jJySixnJbDVPViyHhyLbtQuzMN16oQtQH76839EV9FI6m1DCD67C87KCSdomcYd01jgsntOGPHqBou8AMg67vyA3ZFOFrl_s4F1qxURZw332cji5-j2m=s2048.png\" style=\"width: 346.00px; height: 719.00px; margin-left: 0.00px; margin-top: 0.00px; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px);\" title=\"\"></span></li></ul><ul class=\"c6 lst-kix_nap7staus29z-1\" data-indent=\"1\"><li class=\"c2 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c8\">Use heading 6 to caption images</span></li><li class=\"c2 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c8\">Make images full width and set to “break text”</span></li></ul><ul class=\"c6 lst-kix_nap7staus29z-2 start\" data-indent=\"2\"><li class=\"c7 li-bullet-0\"><span style=\"overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; margin: 0.00px 0.00px; border: 0.00px solid #000000; transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); -webkit-transform: rotate(0.00rad) translateZ(0px); width: 366.00px; height: 159.00px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"images/APuouOebCYF29jB2Ra3XTrUbMyZdsf-99LUI3fMdR_1OEivk2QZiUg0EF16HDQQ6t8I3zOPgzwX09hjaXvZcMwMQIZPOeNssA964buw